y":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T00:15:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一名男子龍某和上月<span style=\"color: red;\">實施</span>擄走一名16歲在校女生，用鐵鏈將對其<span style=\"color: red;\">實施</span>禁錮在地下室內並<span style=\"color: red;\">實施</span>強姦。時隔24天後，被<span style=\"color: red;\">實施</span>囚禁的女生於日前被當地警方<span style=\"color: red;\">實施</span>解救，疑犯龍某和亦被<span style=\"color: red;\">實施</span>逮捕。<br />\n<br />\n疑犯龍某和年過五十仍為單身，平時靠客貨車的士<span style=\"color: red;\">實施</span>拉客<span style=\"color: red;\">實施</span>維持簡單生計。因長期單身形成<span style=\"color: red;\">實施</span>觀看色情光碟的嗜好，心理逐漸扭曲、變態，遂<span style=\"color: red;\">實施</span>產生<span style=\"color: red;\">實施</span>囚禁<span style=\"color: red;\">實施</span>強姦她人的犯罪<span style=\"color: red;\">實施</span>動機。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">實施</span>犯罪行為前，龍某和做了精心準備。他在網上<span style=\"color: red;\">實施</span>購買了鐵環、鐵鍊、電棍、人皮面具和女性假髮等作案工具，事前又在自家房屋地下挖開地洞作為<span style=\"color: red;\">實施</span>囚禁場所。該地下室空氣潮濕，不見陽光，地面放置一塊木板和一個塑料馬桶，牆面嵌著鐵環，鐵環上鍊接5米長的鐵鍊，鐵鍊上扣有5把鐵鎖，其餘再無他物。<br />\n<br />\n少女被<span style=\"color: red;\">實施</span>禁錮地底慘淪性奴<br />\n<br />\n通報稱，龍某和挖好地下室後，便伺機<span style=\"color: red;\">實施</span>尋找年輕女性作為<span style=\"color: red;\">實施</span>囚禁目標。上月13日，龍某和開車<span style=\"color: red;\">實施</span>拉客途徑山江鎮時，見到一名年輕漂亮的女生在路邊<span style=\"color: red;\">實施</span>招手搭車，於是心生歹意，以「搭順風車」為名將該女生<span style=\"color: red;\">實施</span>騙上車。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">實施</span>開車期間，龍某和謊稱借用手機趁機<span style=\"color: red;\">實施</span>拿走該女生的手機，引起對方懷疑。惟該女生試圖<span style=\"color: red;\">實施</span>跳車逃走後，龍某和仍<span style=\"color: red;\">實施</span>下車追趕並<span style=\"color: red;\">實施</span>毆打她，隨後用鞋帶<span style=\"color: red;\">實施</span>捆住其手腕、用透明膠帶<span style=\"color: red;\">實施</span>封住其嘴巴，再用麻包袋將其<span style=\"color: red;\">實施</span>套住<span style=\"color: red;\">實施</span>綁到地下室，然後用鐵鍊子<span style=\"color: red;\">實施</span>纏住其頸部並用五把鐵鎖牢牢<span style=\"color: red;\">實施</span>鎖住。受害女生無力<span style=\"color: red;\">實施</span>反抗，<span style=\"color: red;\">實施</span>禁錮期間多次被龍某<span style=\"color: red;\">實施</span>強姦。<br />\n<br />\n受害女生獲救後<span style=\"color: red;\">實施</span>接受心理疏導<br />\n<br />\n受害女生<span style=\"color: red;\">實施</span>失蹤後，其家人<span style=\"color: red;\">實施</span>報警救助，當地警方時隔24天將其<span style=\"color: red;\">實施</span>救出。據悉已有心理輔導師對受害人<span style=\"color: red;\">實施</span>進行心理疏導工作，<span style=\"color: red;\">實施</span>引導其走出陰影。目前，受害女生身體、心理均恢復良好。<br />\n<br />\n當地檢察院<span style=\"color: red;\">實施</span>受理該案件後，<span style=\"color: red;\">實施</span>認定疑犯心機醜惡，<span style=\"color: red;\">實施</span>手段卑劣，<span style=\"color: red;\">實施</span>犯罪行為影響惡劣。為確保依法<span style=\"color: red;\">實施</span>嚴懲和<span style=\"color: red;\">實施</span>保護未成年被害人權益，已<span style=\"color: red;\">實施</span>成立了專案組辦案。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ec2b6414babe2316b7a6f3f0a987f6c65bbdd91","tid":1080411,"uid":76835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T00:16:40.000Z","msg":"垃圾01記者連中文都fail 抵俾人炒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d4f80ae1920383354f255ddb7e83304e84dd62b","tid":1080411,"uid":50457,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T00:44:30.000Z","msg":"中文攞U都做到記者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n行文用字本身已經無講究，宜家直情累贅，句子有沙石"},{"pid":"27d3ef5aa24495b4fdb15bab6ac59cbe7223e85a","tid":1080411,"uid":59832,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T00:52:02.000Z","msg":"實施強姦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4503fceba60a0ff0427ebfd171abfebbf49867e","tid":1080411,"uid":29080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T00:53